cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL 

The paper discusses the generation of word embeddings from scholarly publications for the intelligent processing of scientific texts, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL). The paper specifically focuses on the analysis of scientific publications, which further supports these categories.
